body.name: YETTASBIN Valentine's Day Rose Gold Cloth Napkins Set of 6, Reusable Washable Oversized Table Napkins for Family Wedding Dinner Party Home Decor, 20 Inch
features: 【PERFECT SIZE】- This cloth napkins measure 20 x 20 Inch/50.5 x 50.5 cm, with exquisite and beautiful 6mm folds. The large size fit your dining table and placemats perfectly, meet all your household needs, they can also be used as hand towels, reduce the use of paper towels, an eco-friendly alternative to paper towels. It looks perfect in your lovely home, both beautiful and practical.

【SOFT CLOTH NAPKINS】- Our Elegant Napkins are made of high-quality durable polyester, which are smooth and soft like silk, lightweight, highly absorbent, quick drying, designed to resist stains and wrinkles. You can make a variety of unique shapes according to your own preferences to match the style you want to make your table setting look stunning.

【EASY TO CARE】- Our Reusable Napkins are easy to clean and can be hand washed or machine washed in cold water, air drying, do not bleach, warm iron if needed. The color is still the same after washing a few times, no fade after repeated use. Reusable, more environmentally friendly and more economical.

【MULTI-PURPOSE】- This cloth napkins are not only suitable for home use, but also perfect for special occasions, such as family dining, festive dinners, wedding, birthday party or any other event, it will enhance the atmosphere at dinning, make your table cozy. Stylish table decorations, can show your elegance, thoughtful gift for your family or friends as housewarming, birthday, Thanksgiving, Christmas or other holiday gifts, enhance dining experience.

【SATISFACTION GUARANTEE】- We always stand behind our high quality Products & Services, if you have any unsatisfied experience on our product, please contact us as soon as possibe we will provide friendly support for you.
